# 🌌 **Nuxora's Quantum Simulator**  
### 🚀 _The easiest way to learn quantum computing_  
[![Python 3.8+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue?logo=python)](https://www.python.org/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)](LICENSE)
[![Downloads](https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/Nuxora/quantum-simulator/total?color=orange)](https://github.com/Nuxora/quantum-simulator/releases)
[![Stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/Nuxora/quantum-simulator?style=social)](https://github.com/Nuxora/quantum-simulator/stargazers)

</div>

## 🔮 **Features** | **Возможности**
| 🇬🇧 English | 🇷🇺 Русский |
|------------|------------|
| ✔️ Simulates 10+ qubits with realistic behavior | ✔️ Реалистичная симуляция 10+ кубитов |
| 🎛️ All basic gates (X, Y, Z, H, CNOT) + advanced (S, T, SWAP) | 🎛️ Все базовые гейты + продвинутые операции |
| 🧠 Grover's and Shor's algorithms ready-to-use | 🧠 Готовые алгоритмы Гровера и Шора |
| 📊 Interactive GUI with Bloch sphere visualization | 📊 Графический интерфейс со сферой Блоха |
| 🎓 Perfect for quantum computing education | 🎓 Идеально для обучения квантовым вычислениям |

## 🛠️ **Quick Start** | **Быстрый старт**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Nuxora/quantum-simulator.git
cd quantum-simulator
pip install -r requirements.txt
python src/gui.py
